Global E-commerce Payment Service Market Insights
E-commerce Payment Service Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 16.5% from 2024 to 2030.

E-commerce Payment Service Market Overview
The global E-commerce Payment Service Market was valued at approximately USD 60 billion in 2023, and it is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 12% from 2024 to 2030. The increasing adoption of digital payment solutions, along with the rise in online shopping and mobile transactions, is fueling the market growth. Furthermore, innovations in payment security technologies, like blockchain and biometrics, are contributing to market expansion. However, challenges such as cyber fraud and regulatory issues in various regions may hamper market growth.

